<TEXT>
while television cameras focused on the leaders 
filmmaker bud greenspan zeroed in on the lastplace runner in the 
5000meter final at the 1984 summer olympics 
dave moorcroft was the world recordholder at the distance but 
injuries had destroyed his chances of winning in los angeles 
